    "en": {
      "title": "This is a top budget budget.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Samagi Jana Balavegaya Kurunegala district councilor Mr. Thushara Indunil said in Parliament today that the government's budget is a top buy budget.",
        "He said this during the second reading debate on the Budget Appropriation Bill.",
        "He said that today Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe is unable to find out whether he is a toy or a bye.",
        "Mr. Thushara Indunil said that today people are suffering in queues and he is questioning who is responsible for this heinous crime."
      ],
